channel.title: Can anyone help me with this error?
channel.description:
Hey I'm adding highscores to my server, and I keep getting this error, and it's kinda pissing me off. =) [code] .\Java\client.java:6789: cannot find symbol symbol : variable objectID location: class client if(objectID == 3192); ^ Note: .\Java\stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
If you could help me, when I have the ability to rep++, I'll rep you.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 13, 2008, 01:32:54 PM[/size][hr]FFS, 10 views no posts, please!
